<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06019001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Rear wheel house front reinforcement is to be reused.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
